<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to ScholarTrack</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* ── Image Protection for Email Clients ── */
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border: 0;
            line-height: 100%;
            outline: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            padding: 40px 16px;
        }

        .wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* ── Header (Light Theme) ── */
        .header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
            padding: 50px 20px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 auto 16px;
        }

        .header-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #475569;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        /* ── Card ── */
        .card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
            padding: 44px 40px 36px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .subtext {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .subtext strong {
            color: #1a1a2e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ── Role Badge ── */
        .role-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EEEDFE, #E1F5EE);
            border: 1px solid #c4b5fd;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #3C3489;
        }

        /* ── Info Box ── */
        .info-box {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }

        .info-row:first-child {
            padding-top: 0;
        }

        .info-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .info-icon.purple { background: #EEEDFE; }
        .info-icon.teal   { background: #E1F5EE; }
        .info-icon.blue   { background: #EFF6FF; }
        .info-icon.rose   { background: #FFE4E6; }

        .info-content {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .info-value {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .password-value {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #3C3489;
            background: #EEEDFE;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* ── Responsibilities List ── */
        .section-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            margin: 28px 0 16px;
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0 0 28px 0;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #525f7f;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .feature-list li::before {
            content: '✓';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            color: #0F6E56; /* Matches your brand green */
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* ── Warning box ── */
        .warning-box {
            background: #fff7ed;
            border-left: 3px solid #f97316;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .warning-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #92400e;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .warning-box p strong {
            color: #c2410c;
        }

        /* ── CTA Button ── */
        .cta-wrapper {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0 24px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3C3489 0%, #0F6E56 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 48px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }

        .cta-subtext {
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .cta-subtext a {
            color: #3C3489;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        /* ── Footer ── */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-divider {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .footer-divider::before,
        .footer-divider::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #9ca3af;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #b0b7c3;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">

        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/3YytxTLh/logo.png" alt="ScholarTrack Logo" width="320"
                    style="display: inline-block; border: none; outline: none; text-decoration: none;" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <span class="header-badge">
                    🎉 Your account is ready
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">

            <p class="greeting">Welcome, <%= name %>! 👋</p>
            <p class="subtext">
                <strong><%= addedByName %></strong> has created a ScholarTrack account for you as a
                <span class="role-badge">Committee Reviewer</span>
            </p>

            <div class="info-box">

                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-icon purple">🏛️</div>
                    <div class="info-content">
                        <div class="info-label">University</div>
                        <div class="info-value"><%= universityName %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-icon teal">📋</div>
                    <div class="info-content">
                        <div class="info-label">Your Role</div>
                        <div class="info-value">Committee Reviewer</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-icon blue">✉️</div>
                    <div class="info-content">
                        <div class="info-label">Login Email</div>
                        <div class="info-value"><%= email %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-icon rose">🔑</div>
                    <div class="info-content">
                        <div class="info-label">Temporary Password</div>
                        <div class="password-value"><%= password %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="section-title">As a Committee Reviewer, your responsibilities include:</div>
            <ul class="feature-list">
                <li>Review scholarship applications across all departments</li>
                <li>Score applicants using a structured rubric</li>
                <li>View AI-generated eligibility scores</li>
                <li>Add detailed evaluation notes</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <p>
                    ⚠️ <strong>Security Notice:</strong> You will be required to change your temporary password immediately upon your first login to secure your account.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-wrapper">
                <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="cta-button">Log In to Your Account</a>
                <p class="cta-subtext">
                    Or copy this link: <a href="<%= loginUrl %>"><%= loginUrl %></a>
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-divider">
                <span class="footer-logo">SCHOLAR TRACK</span>
            </div>
            <p>
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ScholarTrack. All rights reserved.<br>
                This is an automated message — please do not reply directly to this email.
            </p>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
                <a href="#">Help Center</a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>